    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Note that maintenance of those packages have now moved to [`@metamask/json-rpc-engine`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@metamask/json-rpc-engine) and [`@metamask/eth-json-rpc-middleware`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@metamask/eth-json-rpc-middleware), respectively. Some types have moved to [`@metamask/utils`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@metamask/utils), so that may have to be pulled in as well.\r\n\r\nRecently published releases should make migration less off a pain and I'll be keeping an eye on the issue trackers for any issues come up regarding Truffle migrated.",
